Title: Generalized BFT Formalism of Electroweak Theory in the Unitary Gauge
Authors: Yong-Wan Kim, Young-Jai Park and Sean J. Yoon
Comments: 14 pages, Latex, no figures
Report-no: SOGANG-HEP 225/97
Journal-ref: J.Phys. G25 (1999) 1783-1791
\\
  We systematically embed the SU(2)$\times$U(1) Higgs model in the unitary
gauge into a fully gauge-invariant theory by following the generalized BFT
formalism. We also suggest a novel path to get a first-class Lagrangian
directly from the original second-class one using the BFT fields.
